  <th>Percentage of Enrollment Time</th>
  <th>Amount of Tuition Owned to the school</th>
  <tr>
    <td> Less than 10%</td>
    <td> 25%</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td> Less than 50%</td>
    <td> 75%</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td> 50% and more</td>
    <td> 100%</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td colspan="2">First payment of $700 is not refundable after one week</td>
  </tr>
</table>

<h1>Privacy of Information</h1>
<p>
  As a student at <%= @school.name %>, I understand that the school is required to keep records of my progress, attendance, 
  financial obligation, overall performance and other facts as may be necessary while enrolled.  This information is strictly
  protected from inquiry unless I approve of its release.
</p>

<h1>Satisfactory Progress Policy</h1>
<ol>
  <li>All students at <%= @school.name %> must meet a minimum of 2 days per week attendance requirement.</li>
  <li>Your attendance hours will be tracked by beautytrainingsystem.com.  You're only allowed to enter the 
      attendance time for yourself.</li>
  <li>The hours of your attendance will be checked on the 15th of each month.  At that time you will be required to have 
    completed 32 hours for part-time or 80 hours for full-time students.  Any student who does not meet the minimum hours 
    required will be placed on probation for the remainder of the month.
  <li>Your hours will be checked again at the end of each month.  At that time you will need to have at least 64 hours for part-time 
    and 160 hours for full-time students.  Students will be evaluated at the end of every month.  The hours required per
    programs are listed above.
  </li>
  <li>
    If you're on probation for more than 30 business days during your enrollment, you might be terminated or dismissed from the school.
  </li>
  <li>
    You have the right to appeal any decision by submitting a letter requesting a 
    hearing within fifteen (15) days to the school administrator.
  </li>
  <li>This will be documented on your monthly report.  It's very important that you read, understand, 
      and meet the satisfactory progress requirement each month.
  </li>
</ol>

<h1>Financial Obligation Agreement</h1>
<ol>
  <li>Total remaining balance due is payable in monthly installments of $300 per month, 
      due on or before the fifth (5th) of each month.  A late charge of $10.00 will assessed if payment is not received by the due date.
  </li>
  <li>
    I have been enrolled and accepted as a student at <%= @school.name %> and agreed to the payment schedule listed above.
    I will make my payments to <%= @school.name %>.
  </li>
  <li>
    I understand that after satisfactorily completing the minimum requirements as set forth by the 
    Washington State Board and by <%= @school.name %>, I will make full payment of this contract upon my completion 
    of the required hours of my study program.  I will be issued a diploma and a final monthly report which will qualify 
    me to take the Washington State Board's exams.
  </li>
  <li>I agree to pay interest on any amount past due under this contract at the rate of 6% per annum or the maximum rate permitted 
      by WA state law, whichever is less.  I also agree to pay all reasonable collection agency fees, other costs of collections,
      court costs, or attorney fees incurred in the enforcement of this contract.
      This school is a registrant with the Washington State Commission for Education under the Educational Services 
      Registration Act of 1979, and as a student you have certain rights under the laws related to Cosmetologist, Barber,
      Manicurist, Hair Design, Instructor, and Esthetician.
  </li>
  <li>
    I agree that I will use the website beautytrainingsystem.com for my sole and personal study purposes only 
    during the enrollment period.
  </li>
</ol>
<h2 style="color:red;">
  I have read and will comply with the above rules and regulations:<%= f.check_box :contract_agreement %>
</h2>

  <%= f.submit "Submit", class: "btn btn-primary" %>

<% end %>